name: Mooshie's Kitchen 3
storyline: In Mooshie's Kitchen 3, you play as a secret agent whose mission is to infiltrate President Mooshie's bunker and kill Mooshie once and for all!
summary: Mooshie has returned once more in the finale of the Mooshie's Kitchen trilogy. This time, he's the President of the United States!
